'''HomeOS'''是由[[微软研究院|微软研究院]]正在开发的{{le|家庭自动化|home automation}}[[操作系统|操作系统]]的[[暂定名称|暂定名称]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://research.microsoft.com/apps/pubs/default.aspx?id=157701 |title=An Operating System for the Home |last1=Dixon |first1=Colin |last2=Mahajan |first2=Ratul |last3=Agarwal |first3=Sharad |last4=Brush |first4=A.J. |last5=Bongshin |first5=Lee |last6=Saroiu |first6=Stefan |last7=Bahl |first7=Victor |date=April 2012 |work=Microsoft Research – Publications |publisher=[[Microsoft|Microsoft]] |accessdate=26 April 2012 |language=en |archive-date=2013-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023123133/http://research.microsoft.com/apps/pubs/default.aspx?id=157701 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.zdnet.com/blog/microsoft/microsoft-experiments-with-homeos-and-home-app-store-ideas/7352 |title=Microsoft experiments with 'HomeOS' and home app store ideas |last=Foley |first=Mary Jo |date=10 September 2010 |work=All About Microsoft |publisher=ZDNet |accessdate=26 April 2012 |language=en |archive-date=2014-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140105123653/http://www.zdnet.com/blog/microsoft/microsoft-experiments-with-homeos-and-home-app-store-ideas/7352 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，由微软研究院於2010年公布该项目。

== 概要 ==
HomeOS可运行于专门的电脑上，其他各类家庭设备能方便地接入HomeOS，无需作特殊修改<ref name="测试阶段"/>。HomeOS是一个“类PC概念”（PC-like abstraction），主要服务于家庭环境，将家庭生活环境中的各种设备，如[[日光灯|日光灯]]、[[电视机|电视机]]、[[冰箱|冰箱]]和[[洗衣机|洗衣机]]等传统家电及[[手机|手机]]、[[个人电脑|个人电脑]]、[[游戏主机|游戏主机]]等数码产品连接到一台装载HomeOS的机器上，可构成类似当时PC的设备<ref>{{cite web|author=Mary Jo Foley|title=Microsoft boosts HomeOS with a new Lab of Things|url=http://www.cnet.com/news/microsoft-boosts-homeos-with-a-new-lab-of-things/|publisher=CNET|accessdate=2014-04-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140402053302/http://www.cnet.com/news/microsoft-boosts-homeos-with-a-new-lab-of-things/|archivedate=2014-04-02|language=en|date=2013-07-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。依照设计，使用者只需从系统的[[应用商店|应用商店]]HomeStore中下载相应的应用，就可实现如[[远程监控|远程监控]]、设备控制、[[面部识别|面部识别]]等功能<ref>{{cite news|title=微软在官网公布智能家居操作系统报告|url=http://news.dichan.sina.com.cn/2012/05/03/484296.html|accessdate=2014-04-10|newspaper=新浪网|date=2012-05-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120603204051/http://news.dichan.sina.com.cn/2012/05/03/484296.html|archivedate=2012-06-03|language=zh-cn|dead-url=no}}</ref>。HomeOS的开发白皮书中曾明确提出了其使用[[C♯|C#]]和[[.Net_Framework|.Net Framework4.0]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/info/2013-08/30/c_132678115.htm|title=微软谋划智能家居专用操作系统HomeOS|publisher=新华网|work=中国信息产业网|date=2013年8月30日|accessdate=2013-12-07|language=zh-cn|archive-date=2013-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130904101830/http://news.xinhuanet.com/info/2013-08/30/c_132678115.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==沿革==
在2010年，当时微软的研究人员发布了关于HomeOS和HomeStore的白皮书<ref>{{cite web|author=Mary Jo Foley|title=Microsoft's HomeStore: Home automation, with an iPhone-inspired twist|url=http://www.zdnet.com/blog/microsoft/microsofts-homestore-home-automation-with-an-iphone-inspired-twist/7596|publisher=ZDNet|accessdate=2014-04-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103202333/http://www.zdnet.com/blog/microsoft/microsofts-homestore-home-automation-with-an-iphone-inspired-twist/7596|archivedate=2014-01-03|language=en|date=2010-10-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>，名为《 The Home Needs an Operating System (and an App Store)》<ref>{{Cite_web |last1=Dixon |first1=Colin |last2=Mahajan |first2=Ratul |last3=Agarwal |first3=Sharad |last4=Brush |first4=A.J. |last5=Bongshin |first5=Lee |last6=Saroiu |first6=Stefan |last7=Bahl |first7=Victor |title=The Home Needs an Operating System (and an App Store) |url=http://research.microsoft.com/pubs/136890/hotnets2010-homeos.pdf |publisher=Microsoft Research |accessdate=2014-04-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120915034152/http://research.microsoft.com/pubs/136890/hotnets2010-homeos.pdf |archivedate=2012-09-15 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年4月，微软在官网上公布了名为“An Operating System For The Home”（家庭操作系统）的报告，报告中并未提到HomeOS基于什么系统，当时微软的[[Microsoft_Windows|Windows系列]]主要是基于[[NT|NT]]核心，因此有猜测认为HomeOS可能源于Windows<ref name="测试阶段">{{cite news|author=Aimo|title=打造智能家庭 微软HomeOS进入测试阶段|url=http://tech.sina.com.cn/s/2012-04-28/20327038037.shtml|accessdate=2014-04-02|newspaper=新浪网|date=2012-04-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120504144954/http://tech.sina.com.cn/s/2012-04-28/20327038037.shtml|archivedate=2012-05-04|language=zh-cn|dead-url=no}}</ref>。微软在12个实体家庭对全自动化家庭项目模型进行了4到8个月的测试，有42名学生为其开发新应用并使其他额外的设备可以被支持<ref>{{cite news|author=Mary Jo Foley|title=Microsoft forges ahead with new home-automation OS|url=http://www.cnet.com/news/microsoft-forges-ahead-with-new-home-automation-os/|accessdate=2014-04-02|newspaper=CNET|date=April 27, 2012|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140402052704/http://www.cnet.com/news/microsoft-forges-ahead-with-new-home-automation-os/|archivedate=2014-04-02|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年7月的微软年度员工大会上，[[微软研究院|微软研究院]]的Arjmand Samuel宣布了Lab of Things（物联实验室）操作系统，它基于HomeOS但将HomeOS的功能扩展，更适合多个传感器共同协作使用<ref>{{cite news|title=微软将为智能家居提供操作系统|url=http://news.dichan.sina.com.cn/2013/07/31/813985.html|accessdate=2014-04-10|newspaper=新浪网|date=2013-07-31|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140410063247/http://news.dichan.sina.com.cn/2013/07/31/813985.html|archivedate=2014-04-10|language=zh-cn|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

